item.title: i am hungry for launch.
item.description: so we have been workign to launch this search engine for a couple weeks now - and I think we got it. congrats everyone involved. hehe. i have been playing a lot. tonight I made a juke box for some friends, I hooked up my new website, and I slept from 6-10. it ruled. oh and I worked. hehe. a lot going on. check out my bruised elbow. it is madness.
